vulnerabilities.details: Mocodo Mocodo Online 4.2.6 and below does not properly sanitize the `sql_case` input field in `/web/generate.php`, allowing remote attackers to execute arbitrary SQL commands and potentially command injection, leading to remote code execution (RCE) under certain conditions.
